{
  "id": "adv_main_02_10_03",
  "title": "東京編2章23話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "月のテンペスト、三回戦突破、おめでとう！\nよくやったね私達！　かんぱーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Girls‚ congrats on winning the third round! Let’s go‚ Moon Tempest!\nWe did it! Cheers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "かんぱーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、乾杯は全員揃ってからじゃないか？\n買い出し組が、もうすぐ帰ってくるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shouldn’t we toast once everyone gets here?\nThe shopping team should be back anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピに続いて月ストのみなさんも四回戦進出……\nううっ、でも、リズノワは私がミスしたせいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After Sunny Peace‚ Moon Tempest also made it to the fourth round.\nUghh… But not LizNoir‚ and it’s all because I messed up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "まー、まー、勝負は時の運だよー！\n愛ちゃん、めげないめげない。はい、から揚げ食べて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There‚ there. Sometimes it just comes down to luck!\nDon’t let it get you down‚ Ai. Here‚ have some fried chicken.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　LizNoirが凄いのは\nみんな分かってるもん。はい、サラダも～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! Everyone knows\nLizNoir is incredible. Here‚ and some salad‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "き、気持ちは嬉しいんですけど、いっぺんに二つは\nあっ、強引に……んがっ、うぐっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I appreciate you trying to cheer me up‚ but I can’t eat both at the same time…\nHey‚ don’t shove it in… mfff… ughhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん、美味しい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taste good‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.329954656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは！　ほっぺパンパン！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha! Your cheeks are bulging!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4632879893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "――っくん、誰のせいですかあっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*gulp* Whose fault is that?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1966213226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても\n買い出しに行ったみんな、遅いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s odd.\nThe shopping team still hasn’t come home yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "たぶん、買い物に夢中になってるだけだと思うけど……\n一応、見て来るか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure they’re just too focused on the shopping…\nbut I’ll go check on them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0178333715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私も行きます！　きっと荷物一杯だから\n二人の方がいいですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I’ll go as well! I’m sure they’re carrying lots of bags.\nNever hurts to have an extra pair of hands‚ no?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1099546751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな\nじゃあさくら、一緒に行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.\nAlright‚ Sakura. Let’s go together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3546.0543792000008,
          "startTime": 81.3127210459
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3546.0543792000008,
          "startTime": 81.3127210459
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 81.0127210459
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 81.0127210459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "君達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 85.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 85.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんは\n{user}さん、さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening.\n{user}‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "お久しぶり……で、ええのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Long time no see… I guess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 92.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "夜分に申し訳ありません。それから今までずっと\n言えなかったけど、勝手なことしてすみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for coming by at such an hour. And I know this is\nlate in coming‚ but I’m sorry for acting so selfishly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 102.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re all sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 105.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "謝るのは俺の方だ。何も出来なくてごめん\n……君達は星見プロを守ってくれたんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the one who should be apologizing. I’m sorry I couldn’t do anything.\nYou girls were protecting Hoshimi Productions‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 113.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　瑠依ちゃん達の気持ち\nみんな分かってるよ。そんな風に謝らないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! We know why the three of you\ndid what you did. You don’t need to apologize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 120.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nそう言ってもらえると、嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nIt means a lot to hear you say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 124.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、やっぱり星見プロはええな\nあったかいわ～。実家に帰ってきたみたいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Hoshimi Productions really is the best.\nSo warm and cozy. Like coming home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 131.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、そうだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sniffle* Yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 134.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロを出た私達が、再び会いに来ることは\n大変、失礼で申し訳ないことだと思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We know we have no right to come to visit you\nafter having left Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、どうしても、{user}さん\nいえ、星見プロの皆さんに伝えておきたいことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s something we have to tell you.\nNot just you‚ {user}‚ but everyone at Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
