      "text": "私達がアイドルの頂点に立つために、邪魔な存在は\n排除します。たとえ同じ事務所の貴方達でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll eliminate any obstacles that stand in our way to the top‚\nwhether it be idols from our own agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "誤解しないでね。貴方達が憎い訳じゃないの\n私達の目的は、その先にある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get us wrong. We don’t hate you girls.\nOur goal lies beyond.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
