      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリの途中で\n事故死した悲劇のアイドル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The idol who died in a tragic accident\nduring the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "その設定が大衆には非常に受けました。このままでは\n今後、私達がどんな記録を打ち立てても彼女は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A setting that garnered mass public appeal. At this rate‚\nno matter what records we set‚ she will always be seen",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 249.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "私達より上だと、多くの人々は見るでしょう\n――そんなの、おかしい。許せない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "as superior to us by most people.\nIt’s not right—it’s unforgivable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 258.5333333333
