      "text": "kanaはどうでもいいと思うんだけどね～\n死んだ人相手に、そんなにムキにならなくても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Personally‚ I couldn’t care less.\nNo need to get so worked up over a dead person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
