      "text": "私も同感。mihoは昔、長瀬麻奈とひと悶着\nあったんだか知らないけど……理解出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree. Don’t know if you had some sort of beef with Mana Nagase\nwhile she was alive‚ but I don’t get your obsession with her.",
        "id": ""
