      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、長瀬麻奈の伝説を塗り替えたアイドル\nっていうのは、私のキャリアのプラスになる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That said‚ being known as one of the idols who rewrote\nthe legend of Mana Nagase would be a plus for my career.",
