      "text": "故人をそんな風に言わないで下さい！\n彼女は、間違いなく凄いアイドルでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t speak of the dead that way!\nShe was‚ without a doubt‚ an incredible idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
